      <title>英国通胀挂钩债券收益率创 2022 年特拉斯崩盘以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/uk-inflation-linked-yields-hit-highest-since-truss-s-2022-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国30年期通胀保值债券收益率自2022年底市场崩盘以来首次升至2%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/uk-inflation-linked-yields-hit-highest-since-truss-s-2022-rout</guid>
