    <item>
      <title>据当地媒体报道，印尼将把一年的出口收入转回国内</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/indonesia-to-make-export-earnings-kept-home-for-a-year-kontan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地新闻媒体 Kontan 援引一位高级部长的话报道，印尼将要求自然资源出口商将部分外汇收入留在境内至少一年，以增加外汇储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/indonesia-to-make-export-earnings-kept-home-for-a-year-kontan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 10:08:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>借贷成本飙升，英国发行 42.5 亿英镑五年期债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/uk-prepares-to-sell-new-five-year-bonds-as-borrowing-costs-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国周三出售了 42.5 亿英镑（53 亿美元）的五年期债券，这是十多年来英国最大的一次五年期债券出售，因为借贷成本的飙升使政府的融资计划变得复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/uk-prepares-to-sell-new-five-year-bonds-as-borrowing-costs-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 09:14:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡行长称通货紧缩将带来“一些喘息机会”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/deflation-to-provide-respite-to-sri-lankans-says-governor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡央行行长表示，该国的通货紧缩环境预计将持续到 2025 年初，这凸显了这个南亚国家在前所未有的经济危机中苦苦挣扎于高物价的状况的变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/deflation-to-provide-respite-to-sri-lankans-says-governor</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 08:38:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>壳牌预计 2024 年天然气收益将下降，因业绩不佳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/shell-flags-lower-gas-volumes-weaker-trading-in-fourth-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[壳牌公司表示，其天然气部门的销售量和交易收入均有所下降，这是表明 2024 年对于主要能源公司来说将以疲软的业绩结束的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/shell-flags-lower-gas-volumes-weaker-trading-in-fourth-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 07:11:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>被美国列入黑名单后，腾讯进行 2006 年以来最大规模股票回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/tencent-makes-biggest-buyback-since-2006-after-us-blacklist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[腾讯控股有限公司因涉嫌与中国军方有联系而被列入美国黑名单，引发股价下跌，随后该公司回购了近二十年来最多数量的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/tencent-makes-biggest-buyback-since-2006-after-us-blacklist</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 01:42:42 GMT</pubDate>
